          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Find & Verify</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Search verified suppliers by trust score, certifications, and supply chain history.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="group relative bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 hover:border-accent-500/30 rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-5xl font-black text-white/[0.03]">02</div>
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-accent-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-accent-500/20 transition-colors">
            <i data-lucide="lock" class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-400"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Escrow Lock</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Funds are locked in a smart contract escrow until delivery is confirmed and verified.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="group relative bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/5 hover:border-yellow-500/30 rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-5xl font-black text-white/[0.03]">03</div>
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-yellow-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-yellow-500/20 transition-colors">
            <i data-lucide="scan-line" class="w-6 h-6 text-yellow-400"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Ship & Track</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Real-time supply chain tracking with IoT verification at every checkpoint.</p>
        </div>

